paragraph.text:
Any federally owned lands that have been or hereafter may be acquired for National Forest System purposes within the boundaries of Cibola National Forest, as modified by subsection (a), shall be managed as lands acquired under the 
              Act of March 1, 1911 (commonly known as the Weeks Act; 
              16 U.S.C. 515 et seq.), and in accordance with the other laws and regulations pertaining to the National Forest System.
